Name:           hinduce-classifier-decisiontree
Version:        0.0.0.0
License:        BSD3
Author:         Robert Hensing
Maintainer:     hackage@roberthensing.nl
Synopsis:       Decision Tree Classifiers for hInduce
Description:    A very simple decision tree construction algorithm; an implementation of @hinduce-classifier@'s @Classifier@ class.
Stability:      functional but lacking
Maintainer:     Robert Hensing
Build-Type:     Simple
Cabal-Version:  >= 1.4
Category:       Data Mining

Library
    Build-Depends:      base >= 4 && < 5,
                        layout >= 0.0.0.1,
                        hinduce-missingh >= 0.0.0.0,
                        hinduce-classifier >= 0.0.0.0,
                        convertible
    Exposed-Modules:    Data.HInduce.Classifier.DecisionTree
    Hs-Source-Dirs:     src
    Extensions:	        MultiParamTypeClasses, FunctionalDependencies, FlexibleInstances, UndecidableInstances, TupleSections, TypeSynonymInstances
